title: Reccomendation System
subtitle: User-to-User Collaborative Filtering
description: Reccomend new movies to users based on the preferences of similar users. Cosine similarity is used to form the neighbourhood of similar users.

title: Diagnostic System
subtitle: Classification of Malignant cells
description: Implemented a diagnostic system using a Rule-based Classifier, Random Forest Classifier and Gaussian Naive Bayes to classify malignant cells and evaluated each model's performance.
